        <title>The span module </title>
        <annotation annotates="/">
            <para>This module defines the span element for grouping inline content. </para>
            <para>More information about this module is available at http://www.daisy.org/z3998/2012/auth/cm/#z3998.span.module</para>
        </annotation>
